WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-

2
00:00:30.321 --> 00:00:31.197
Sup!

3
00:00:31.281 --> 00:00:32.407
Hey. Morimo!

4
00:00:36.327 --> 00:00:37.787
-Morning.
-Sup!

5
00:00:37.871 --> 00:00:39.664
-Hey. Mini! Sup!
-What're you doing?

6
00:00:39.748 --> 00:00:40.915
Goofing off.

7
00:01:20.997 --> 00:01:22.916
Tani-kun! Morning!

8
00:01:26.002 --> 00:01:28.087
Morning!

9
00:01:28.171 --> 00:01:29.172
That's so creepy.

10
00:01:29.255 --> 00:01:30.423
No one asked you!

11
00:01:30.507 --> 00:01:32.592
Move or I'll crush
those hair buns of yours!

12
00:01:32.675 --> 00:01:33.551
Stop it!

13
00:01:33.635 --> 00:01:36.429
If you two don't hurry up. you'll be late!

14
00:01:37.305 --> 00:01:38.431
I'm going!

15
00:01:56.783 --> 00:01:58.326
Morning. Suzuki.

16
00:01:58.409 --> 00:01:59.744
Oh. Azuma! Morning.

17
00:01:59.828 --> 00:02:00.745
You and Taira came together?

18
00:02:00.829 --> 00:02:01.830
We did not!

19
00:02:01.913 --> 00:02:03.581
Morning. Nabesato!

20
00:02:03.665 --> 00:02:04.833
-Morning.
-Good morning!

21
00:02:04.916 --> 00:02:06.584
Hey there. Yamada!

22
00:02:06.668 --> 00:02:07.585
Hey!

23
00:02:07.669 --> 00:02:10.839
Oh! T… Tani-kun! Good morning!

24
00:02:15.009 --> 00:02:16.094
Good morning.

25
00:02:18.680 --> 00:02:20.640
Suzuki. you're so loud!

26
00:02:20.723 --> 00:02:22.600
Proper greetings will save the world!

27
00:02:22.684 --> 00:02:25.645
Hey. my eyelashes look good today. right?

28
00:02:26.354 --> 00:02:27.730
I can't tell.

29
00:02:28.314 --> 00:02:29.482
Why not just use false eyelashes?

30
00:02:30.066 --> 00:02:35.613
I could. but I prefer my real eyelashes.

31
00:02:35.697 --> 00:02:40.702
And the mascara comes off
if you sweat. cry. or rub it.

32
00:02:40.785 --> 00:02:44.122
So. I just end up wondering
which brand I should try…

33
00:02:44.205 --> 00:02:47.125
and stuff like that.

34
00:02:47.208 --> 00:02:48.918
Tani-kun. what do you think?

35
00:02:51.045 --> 00:02:52.881
I wouldn't know anything
about it. would I?

36
00:02:54.757 --> 00:02:57.385
Tani-kun! You're as icy as always today!

37
00:02:57.468 --> 00:03:00.138
Why do you get such a kick
out of pestering Tani-kun

38
00:03:00.221 --> 00:03:01.973
about things he obviously
has no interest in.

39
00:03:02.056 --> 00:03:02.891
Exactly.

40
00:03:02.974 --> 00:03:07.520
I love the way he shuts me down.
I can't help myself.

41
00:03:08.271 --> 00:03:11.024
If you ever need help
picking mascara. I'll help!

42
00:03:11.107 --> 00:03:12.275
No need.

43
00:03:12.358 --> 00:03:14.193
Shut down again!

44
00:03:14.277 --> 00:03:15.653
He's ruthless.

45
00:03:15.737 --> 00:03:17.405
Stop bothering Tani-kun.

46
00:03:22.744 --> 00:03:26.706
<i>Tani-kun. I'm so sorry. Truly.</i>

47
00:03:27.415 --> 00:03:28.958
<i>To be honest…</i>

48
00:03:30.251 --> 00:03:32.295
<i>I'm desperately in love with you!</i>

49
00:05:05.013 --> 00:05:06.597
Did you finish your English homework?

50
00:05:06.681 --> 00:05:09.017
I only did the parts
I thought I might get right.

51
00:05:09.100 --> 00:05:10.518
Do the whole thing.

52
00:05:11.102 --> 00:05:13.021
<i>Sitting in the seat next</i>
<i>to mine is Tani-kun.</i>

53
00:05:13.521 --> 00:05:19.944
<i>He seems like a quiet guy</i>
<i>with glasses to everyone else.</i>

54
00:05:20.028 --> 00:05:22.947
{\an8}<i>but Tani-kun speaks his mind clearly.</i>

55
00:05:23.031 --> 00:05:23.948
THWACK

56
00:05:24.032 --> 00:05:27.035
The teacher will probably flag this part.
so it needs to be redone.

57
00:05:27.118 --> 00:05:29.454
Huh? Why? Good enough
is good enough. right?

58
00:05:30.038 --> 00:05:32.957
<i>And he has the same attitude</i>
<i>no matter who he's with.</i>

59
00:05:33.041 --> 00:05:33.833
HE'S NOT PUSHY. THOUGH

60
00:05:33.916 --> 00:05:34.751
Do you have your assignment?

61
00:05:34.834 --> 00:05:35.668
FWIP…

62
00:05:35.752 --> 00:05:36.586
HE DOESN'T GROVEL. EITHER
FWIP…

63
00:05:36.669 --> 00:05:37.712
Assignment?

64
00:05:37.795 --> 00:05:39.088
Thanks for collecting them.

65
00:05:39.172 --> 00:05:40.590
Thanks.

66
00:05:41.299 --> 00:05:43.593
<i>Like the last time we changed seats…</i>

67
00:05:43.676 --> 00:05:44.510
{\an8}FRONT
BACK

68
00:05:44.594 --> 00:05:46.888
{\an8}Okay. Change seats.

69
00:05:53.686 --> 00:05:56.355
A MIRACLE

70
00:05:57.774 --> 00:05:58.983
{\an8}<i>I'm right next to him!</i>

71
00:05:59.067 --> 00:06:00.902
{\an8}<i>This is crazy. What do I do?!</i>

72
00:06:01.944 --> 00:06:04.280
{\an8}I hope you'll treat me well. neighbor!

73
00:06:04.363 --> 00:06:05.281
{\an8}TENSE… SMILE…

74
00:06:05.364 --> 00:06:06.199
{\an8}Likewise.

75
00:06:06.699 --> 00:06:08.868
The thing about being in the front row…

76
00:06:08.951 --> 00:06:11.871
The blackboard can be harder to read
that you'd expect.

77
00:06:12.455 --> 00:06:14.874
I'll read anything
you can't make out. 'kay?

78
00:06:15.583 --> 00:06:17.293
I think I'll be fine.

79
00:06:17.376 --> 00:06:18.878
Okay. then!

80
00:06:19.378 --> 00:06:23.049
<i>Tani-kun doesn't adjust his behavior</i>
<i>without good reason.</i>

81
00:06:24.550 --> 00:06:28.054
<i>I just really… really admire that!</i>

82
00:06:28.137 --> 00:06:30.389
Suzuki. which one do you like?

83
00:06:31.224 --> 00:06:32.433
Sorry. I wasn't listening!

84
00:06:33.226 --> 00:06:35.269
B… But. I mean…

85
00:06:35.353 --> 00:06:36.479
I think that a person

86
00:06:36.562 --> 00:06:39.398
would rev up the crowd better
than an audio recording.

87
00:06:39.482 --> 00:06:40.900
Right. Tani-kun?

88
00:06:40.983 --> 00:06:42.485
I have no idea.

89
00:06:42.568 --> 00:06:46.572
Tani-kun. if she's bothering you.
just say so.

90
00:06:49.325 --> 00:06:50.910
It's fine.

91
00:06:52.745 --> 00:06:54.747
See? He says it's fine!

92
00:06:54.831 --> 00:06:57.416
<i>Whew! What a relief!</i>

93
00:06:58.126 --> 00:07:01.045
<i>Tani-kun. I'm sorry! I love you. and yet…</i>

94
00:07:01.129 --> 00:07:03.381
<i>I want to talk to you normally. and yet…</i>

95
00:07:03.881 --> 00:07:06.259
<i>I'm always worrying about</i>
<i>how others see me.</i>

96
00:07:06.342 --> 00:07:10.304
<i>so I can't talk in a way</i>
<i>that reveals that I like you!</i>

97
00:07:10.388 --> 00:07:14.350
<i>I admire Tani-kun so much. but…</i>

98
00:07:14.434 --> 00:07:16.894
<i>you and I are polar opposites!</i>

99
00:07:17.937 --> 00:07:20.356
Right! After school.
let's all go to KingBurg!

100
00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:21.941
Hey. Suzuki! You'll come too. right?

101
00:07:23.025 --> 00:07:24.944
<i>I have to do my homework.</i>

102
00:07:25.027 --> 00:07:27.447
EXCITED

103
00:07:30.533 --> 00:07:32.243
I'm totally going!

104
00:07:32.326 --> 00:07:34.454
{\an8}Yay!

105
00:07:35.496 --> 00:07:38.207
Suzuki. will you let me
copy your homework?

106
00:07:38.291 --> 00:07:39.750
Again?

107
00:07:39.834 --> 00:07:40.918
Please save me!

108
00:07:41.919 --> 00:07:43.796
{\an8}Oh. fine. You're hopeless!

109
00:07:43.880 --> 00:07:45.089
{\an8}Thank you!

110
00:07:45.756 --> 00:07:49.510
Oh. Suzuki! Your story yesterday
made me laugh!

111
00:07:49.594 --> 00:07:51.596
Suzuki-san. do you mind
if I follow your account too?

112
00:07:52.180 --> 00:07:54.015
<i>I didn't post anything weird. did I?</i>

113
00:07:54.098 --> 00:07:56.976
Sure! Please do!

114
00:07:57.643 --> 00:07:58.478
But. you know…

115
00:07:58.561 --> 00:08:00.938
Tani's really smart. right?

116
00:08:02.815 --> 00:08:04.567
Are you talking about
the group work today?

117
00:08:04.650 --> 00:08:06.736
Now that you mention it.
I saw him heading to cram school.

118
00:08:07.445 --> 00:08:08.571
Is he headed for UTokyo?

119
00:08:08.654 --> 00:08:09.989
I don't know about that.

120
00:08:10.072 --> 00:08:12.116
He's really amazing. isn't he?

121
00:08:12.200 --> 00:08:15.161
He lives in a different world
from the rest of us.

122
00:08:15.244 --> 00:08:16.245
Don't lump me in with you.

123
00:08:16.829 --> 00:08:20.291
Suzuki's the closest to Tani-kun
in our group. right?

124
00:08:20.374 --> 00:08:22.710
What? You think so?

125
00:08:24.879 --> 00:08:26.005
That's gross!

126
00:08:26.088 --> 00:08:27.006
Are you okay?

127
00:08:28.216 --> 00:08:31.969
I'm just at an age when stuff
catches in my throat easily.

128
00:08:32.053 --> 00:08:33.012
You're too young for that.

129
00:08:34.430 --> 00:08:37.517
Oh! SudaKen won Most Beloved Actor
for a second time!

130
00:08:38.309 --> 00:08:40.269
Girls really like
the mischievous types. huh?

131
00:08:40.353 --> 00:08:43.105
Whoa. SudaKen's the only one
who's boyfriend material.

132
00:08:43.189 --> 00:08:45.525
There it is! Suzuki's
stanning SudaKen again.

133
00:08:48.819 --> 00:08:51.781
<i>Some say reading the room</i>
<i>is for other people's sakes…</i>

134
00:08:52.740 --> 00:08:54.075
<i>but it isn't.</i>

135
00:08:55.493 --> 00:08:57.870
<i>I do it completely for my own sake.</i>

136
00:09:06.671 --> 00:09:07.755
<i>And yet…</i>

137
00:09:09.257 --> 00:09:13.177
<i>sometimes it tires me out. Why is that?</i>

138
00:09:20.977 --> 00:09:22.853
<i>I should head home.</i>

139
00:09:34.407 --> 00:09:36.951
T… Tani-kun. are you heading home now?
It's late. isn't it?

140
00:09:37.535 --> 00:09:39.954
<i>I know my face must've</i>
<i>looked hideous just now!</i>

141
00:09:41.038 --> 00:09:42.957
There was committee work to be submitted.

142
00:09:43.624 --> 00:09:46.335
Tani-kun. what way do you take home?

143
00:09:46.419 --> 00:09:47.837
Out the gate and turn right.

144
00:09:48.379 --> 00:09:49.213
Same!

145
00:09:49.297 --> 00:09:51.465
<i>No one's watching.</i>

146
00:09:54.051 --> 00:09:54.969
Tani-kun…

147
00:09:56.470 --> 00:09:57.555
This is crazy!

148
00:10:00.308 --> 00:10:03.227
Want to go part of the way home together?

149
00:10:03.853 --> 00:10:06.105
<i>My heart's gonna burst out of my chest!</i>

150
00:10:08.357 --> 00:10:10.735
So. Tani-kun. your house is this way too?

151
00:10:10.818 --> 00:10:12.987
We've never ended up
together before. though.

152
00:10:14.030 --> 00:10:14.864
Yeah.

153
00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:24.206
Oh. I'm always running around
goofing off after school.

154
00:10:24.290 --> 00:10:25.666
No wonder I never saw you.

155
00:10:25.750 --> 00:10:28.377
And you have student council stuff
to do too. right?

156
00:10:29.962 --> 00:10:30.838
Yeah.

157
00:10:39.722 --> 00:10:42.975
And. um. we went to KingBurg
the other day.

158
00:10:43.059 --> 00:10:46.729
and the burger was huge!
It didn't even fit in the bun.

159
00:10:46.812 --> 00:10:49.190
The buns were basically
served on the side. you know?

160
00:10:49.273 --> 00:10:52.109
I had no idea how to eat it!

161
00:10:53.319 --> 00:10:55.071
<i>Wait. Is this topic interesting at all?</i>

162
00:10:55.571 --> 00:10:56.656
Was it good?

163
00:10:58.366 --> 00:11:00.534
Yeah! It was! Super good!

164
00:11:00.618 --> 00:11:04.664
I know! Tani-kun. want to
grab one with me? Just kidding!

165
00:11:05.289 --> 00:11:06.165
Sure.

166
00:11:10.419 --> 00:11:11.629
<i>What did he just say?</i>

167
00:11:12.129 --> 00:11:15.299
<i>Is he just being polite?</i>
<i>Or matching the mood?</i>

168
00:11:18.636 --> 00:11:21.806
<i>No. Tani-kun isn't that kind of person.</i>

169
00:11:30.147 --> 00:11:31.440
<i>Find something…</i>

170
00:11:31.524 --> 00:11:34.026
<i>Say something back to him. me!</i>

171
00:11:34.527 --> 00:11:35.694
<i>It's no good!</i>

172
00:11:35.778 --> 00:11:39.198
{\an8}<i>My heart is pounding so hard!</i>
<i>I just can't!</i>

173
00:11:39.281 --> 00:11:40.449
{\an8}BONK

174
00:11:40.533 --> 00:11:42.076
SHOCK

175
00:11:43.202 --> 00:11:44.412
Uh. um. I…

176
00:12:18.571 --> 00:12:19.738
<i>It can't be.</i>

177
00:12:21.365 --> 00:12:22.533
<i>What is this?</i>

178
00:12:23.159 --> 00:12:24.201
<i>A dream?</i>

179
00:12:26.829 --> 00:12:30.040
<i>What? What do I do? Right now. I'm…</i>

180
00:12:31.333 --> 00:12:32.960
<i>I'm certain my hand is</i>
<i>sweating like crazy.</i>

181
00:12:35.296 --> 00:12:39.300
<i>My heartbeat is so loud</i>
<i>I can hear it pounding in my ears!</i>

182
00:12:39.383 --> 00:12:40.342
<i>Am I dying?</i>

183
00:12:40.843 --> 00:12:44.346
Harasen's bangs look really weird.

184
00:12:44.430 --> 00:12:45.848
They look really bad.

185
00:12:53.856 --> 00:12:54.565
{\an8}I THINK WE PROBABLY SAID SOMETHING
LIKE THIS - I'M THIS WAY…

186
00:12:54.648 --> 00:12:55.733
{\an8}<i>I don't remember how…</i>

187
00:12:55.816 --> 00:12:56.650
{\an8}OH! I'M GOING THE OTHER DIRECTION!

188
00:12:56.734 --> 00:12:58.903
{\an8}<i>…I got home after that.</i>

189
00:12:58.986 --> 00:13:00.279
{\an8}-TANI-KUN. SEE YOU LATER!
-YEAH. LATER…

190
00:13:03.824 --> 00:13:06.452
I'm ho--! Don't lie in the entryway!

191
00:13:06.535 --> 00:13:07.369
GLOOM

192
00:13:07.453 --> 00:13:09.371
Oh. Nii-chan.

193
00:13:11.957 --> 00:13:13.125
FLAIL GYAAAAAAH

194
00:13:13.209 --> 00:13:14.376
<i>Creepy!</i>

195
00:13:16.170 --> 00:13:19.089
<i>We… held hands.</i>

196
00:13:19.173 --> 00:13:20.424
Aren't you going to eat?

197
00:13:20.508 --> 00:13:22.134
If you're not gonna eat. then gimme!

198
00:13:23.177 --> 00:13:24.637
<i>And…</i>

199
00:13:25.221 --> 00:13:26.639
<i>he grabbed my hand!</i>

200
00:13:26.722 --> 00:13:29.225
<i>This is crazy! This is crazy!</i>
<i>This is crazy!</i>

201
00:13:29.308 --> 00:13:32.394
<i>How do I face everyone at school tomorrow?</i>

202
00:13:32.978 --> 00:13:36.649
{\an8}<i>My heart is racing so fast!</i>
<i>I'll never get to sleep!</i>

203
00:13:37.566 --> 00:13:40.444
AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAH

204
00:13:40.528 --> 00:13:42.279
Shut up!

205
00:13:42.988 --> 00:13:45.533
SNORE

206
00:13:45.616 --> 00:13:47.910
ZZZZZZZZZZZZ…

207
00:13:54.625 --> 00:13:55.459
{\an8}Ow!

208
00:13:56.043 --> 00:13:58.045
Owww…

209
00:13:58.128 --> 00:14:00.381
Morning? You're kidding.

210
00:14:00.464 --> 00:14:01.715
Wait. What time is it?

211
00:14:07.054 --> 00:14:07.888
{\an8}TMPTMPTMPTMPTMPTMPTMP

212
00:14:07.972 --> 00:14:09.974
{\an8}I didn't have any absences or tardies yet!

213
00:14:10.933 --> 00:14:12.810
What?! Where is everyone?

214
00:14:12.893 --> 00:14:14.228
EVERYONE
BROTHER. MOM. DAD

215
00:14:14.311 --> 00:14:15.896
{\an8}IT'S ALL RIGHT TO BE LATE SOMETIMES.
BUT MAKE SURE YOU EAT BREAKFAST. MOM

216
00:14:15.980 --> 00:14:18.232
{\an8}Mom!

217
00:14:18.899 --> 00:14:20.985
And it's more like midday
than morning now.

218
00:14:22.027 --> 00:14:22.862
{\an8}BEING RIDICULOUSLY LATE
ACTUALLY RELAXES HER

219
00:14:22.945 --> 00:14:24.989
{\an8}I get the feeling
hurrying won't change anything.

220
00:14:26.240 --> 00:14:27.241
Let's microwave this.

221
00:14:30.536 --> 00:14:32.580
It's already lunchtime. but good morning!

222
00:14:32.663 --> 00:14:34.248
Suzuki. it's rare for you to be late.

223
00:14:34.331 --> 00:14:36.625
You could've just taken
the day off at this point.

224
00:14:36.709 --> 00:14:39.003
But I want to do
our elective PE class. you know?

225
00:14:39.086 --> 00:14:40.004
What a moron.

226
00:14:43.299 --> 00:14:44.967
Oh. Suzuki! You're here!

227
00:14:45.050 --> 00:14:46.135
Yeah! Sup!

228
00:14:46.886 --> 00:14:50.764
Hey. are you and Tani dating?

229
00:14:51.724 --> 00:14:52.600
{\an8}<i>Huh?</i>

230
00:14:53.475 --> 00:14:57.479
Gapacho said you two walked
home together yesterday.

231
00:14:57.563 --> 00:14:58.772
<i>Who the heck is Gapacho?</i>

232
00:14:58.856 --> 00:15:00.608
It wasn't someone else?

233
00:15:00.691 --> 00:15:02.192
Gapacho knows what he saw!

234
00:15:02.276 --> 00:15:03.402
Not our concern.

235
00:15:04.069 --> 00:15:06.155
<i>Hey. hey. hang on. Yamada.</i>

236
00:15:06.822 --> 00:15:07.698
<i>Right now.</i>

237
00:15:07.781 --> 00:15:11.911
<i>we're in the "might be mutual.</i>
<i>but not yet confirmed" phase.</i>

238
00:15:11.994 --> 00:15:13.913
<i>The most delicate phase of all!</i>

239
00:15:13.996 --> 00:15:16.582
<i>It's not something</i>
<i>you can poke at for fun!</i>

240
00:15:16.665 --> 00:15:18.417
<i>I'm playing for keeps here!</i>

241
00:15:19.919 --> 00:15:21.420
<i>And. I mean…</i>

242
00:15:22.254 --> 00:15:24.173
<i>-someone saw us.</i>
-So?

243
00:15:24.882 --> 00:15:26.133
<i>Saw us where?</i>

244
00:15:28.761 --> 00:15:31.138
Oh. um…

245
00:15:37.770 --> 00:15:39.521
It's not like that!

246
00:15:40.314 --> 00:15:41.398
You know…

247
00:15:42.983 --> 00:15:45.319
That's my seat.

248
00:15:48.489 --> 00:15:49.490
Can I grab my notebook?

249
00:15:50.324 --> 00:15:51.575
Oh. sorry. I'll move.

250
00:15:51.659 --> 00:15:53.661
It's fine. We go somewhere else
next period.

251
00:15:53.744 --> 00:15:54.578
R… Right.

252
00:16:05.214 --> 00:16:07.007
<i>It couldn't be worse.</i>

253
00:16:09.677 --> 00:16:12.096
The body breaks down carbohydrates.

254
00:16:12.179 --> 00:16:14.306
and blood sugar levels rise.

255
00:16:14.390 --> 00:16:17.601
<i>He heard me denying it.</i>

256
00:16:17.685 --> 00:16:19.603
<i>It was so beyond rude!</i>

257
00:16:21.105 --> 00:16:23.983
You have it all wrong!
I didn't mean to say it like that!

258
00:16:24.066 --> 00:16:25.359
Tani-kun. I'm so sorry…

259
00:16:29.446 --> 00:16:31.198
{\an8}<i>No. no. no! I could never!</i>

260
00:16:31.281 --> 00:16:33.492
{\an8}<i>But I want to apologize ASAP!</i>

261
00:16:35.327 --> 00:16:36.996
{\an8}<i>What do I do?</i>

262
00:16:37.079 --> 00:16:40.124
{\an8}<i>I hope Tani-kun</i>
<i>doesn't feel awful right now.</i>

263
00:16:40.207 --> 00:16:41.041
{\an8}<i>I hate this.</i>

264
00:16:41.125 --> 00:16:43.877
{\an8}Suzuki. you haven't picked up
any of the shuttles!

265
00:16:43.961 --> 00:16:45.129
Just pick 'em up with your hands!

266
00:16:45.212 --> 00:16:47.589
{\an8}ANGST ANGST

267
00:16:47.673 --> 00:16:50.384
{\an8}<i>Oh. why am I always so…</i>

268
00:16:51.719 --> 00:16:53.637
Sorry. Suzuki!

269
00:16:58.809 --> 00:17:00.269
{\an8}<i>Talk.</i>

270
00:17:00.352 --> 00:17:01.854
<i>I have to talk to him!</i>

271
00:17:01.937 --> 00:17:03.647
<i>Hurry up and explain</i>
<i>this misunderstanding!</i>

272
00:17:05.482 --> 00:17:07.151
<i>But… here?</i>

273
00:17:08.318 --> 00:17:10.487
{\an8}<i>Here. where everyone else is?</i>

274
00:17:16.243 --> 00:17:17.411
Suzuki-san.

275
00:17:17.494 --> 00:17:18.412
BA-DUMP

276
00:17:19.121 --> 00:17:20.497
T… Tani-ku…

277
00:17:24.001 --> 00:17:26.295
Please forget what happened yesterday.

278
00:17:27.713 --> 00:17:28.589
I'm sorry.

279
00:17:43.395 --> 00:17:47.066
Come on. Suzuki!
This popcorn coupon expires today!

280
00:17:47.149 --> 00:17:50.110
{\an8}Hey. weren't you just talking to Tani-kun?

281
00:17:50.194 --> 00:17:51.779
{\an8}You really do get along. huh?

282
00:17:52.905 --> 00:17:54.073
Suzuki?

283
00:17:54.656 --> 00:17:55.574
You too?

284
00:17:55.657 --> 00:17:57.076
Do it again! Do it again!

285
00:18:04.917 --> 00:18:05.918
I…

286
00:18:06.418 --> 00:18:09.379
am in love with Tani-kun.

287
00:18:09.463 --> 00:18:10.297
What?

288
00:18:10.923 --> 00:18:12.674
It's a one-sided love.

289
00:18:14.968 --> 00:18:20.599
And yesterday… I invited him
to walk home with me.

290
00:18:21.558 --> 00:18:24.853
Is that… wrong somehow?

291
00:18:27.272 --> 00:18:28.148
SO LOUD…

292
00:18:28.232 --> 00:18:30.275
What? You should've told me!

293
00:18:30.359 --> 00:18:33.070
Anyone would think
you just met up on the way home!

294
00:18:33.153 --> 00:18:36.281
Who would think it
was a serious situation?!

295
00:18:36.365 --> 00:18:37.491
Huh? Hang on.

296
00:18:37.574 --> 00:18:41.578
{\an8}I feel like I said
something majorly insensitive at lunch.

297
00:18:41.662 --> 00:18:43.372
{\an8}You're always insensitive.

298
00:18:44.289 --> 00:18:47.167
So. Tani-kun already left. Is that okay?

299
00:18:47.251 --> 00:18:48.127
It's not okay!

300
00:18:48.210 --> 00:18:50.003
You might make it if you run!

301
00:18:50.087 --> 00:18:51.880
This is major. Suzuki! Go get 'em!

302
00:18:55.092 --> 00:18:57.678
Don't worry about the popcorn!

303
00:18:57.761 --> 00:18:59.513
-Sorry! I really don't care!
-Hey!

304
00:19:01.515 --> 00:19:05.018
Run. Suzuki! Show us speed
that won't shame your name!

305
00:19:05.102 --> 00:19:07.062
You're a Suzuki. right?

306
00:19:09.356 --> 00:19:10.315
{\an8}SLOW

307
00:19:10.399 --> 00:19:11.650
{\an8}How slow can you be?

308
00:19:13.360 --> 00:19:15.779
-Hit 'im hard!
-Look ahead of you!

309
00:19:15.863 --> 00:19:17.906
Go!

310
00:19:20.617 --> 00:19:21.994
<i>What's this?</i>

311
00:19:24.413 --> 00:19:26.999
<i>Saying how I feel out loud…</i>

312
00:19:27.082 --> 00:19:29.877
<i>was this easy to do?</i>

313
00:19:42.639 --> 00:19:43.807
{\an8}<i>I gave in to temptation.</i>

314
00:19:43.891 --> 00:19:44.725
{\an8}NO USE REGRETTING IT NOW…

315
00:19:44.808 --> 00:19:46.560
{\an8}<i>That's all I can say.</i>

316
00:19:47.144 --> 00:19:51.398
<i>Suzuki-san sits next to me.</i>
<i>She always talks to me.</i>

317
00:19:51.481 --> 00:19:55.444
<i>but she doesn't care about me personally.</i>

318
00:19:55.527 --> 00:19:56.653
<i>It's just light banter.</i>

319
00:19:58.488 --> 00:20:01.283
Want to go part of the way home together?

320
00:20:01.783 --> 00:20:04.077
<i>That's what I thought. but…</i>

321
00:20:18.800 --> 00:20:21.845
<i>Today…</i>
<i>I thought she might not come to school.</i>

322
00:20:22.429 --> 00:20:24.348
It's not like that!

323
00:20:26.558 --> 00:20:31.104
<i>Pretty soon. I grew used to</i>
<i>Suzuki-san talking to me.</i>

324
00:20:32.940 --> 00:20:35.108
<i>A day without her…</i>

325
00:20:35.192 --> 00:20:36.193
Tani-kun!

326
00:20:36.276 --> 00:20:38.612
<i>…is just too quiet.</i>

327
00:20:38.695 --> 00:20:43.617
I love you!

328
00:20:51.333 --> 00:20:57.130
T… Tani-kun. sorry that I pester you
with stupid stuff.

329
00:20:57.798 --> 00:21:01.635
And I'm sorry for what I said
in front of everyone today!

330
00:21:01.718 --> 00:21:05.222
I didn't know how to
talk to you. Tani-kun.

331
00:21:06.765 --> 00:21:10.727
I was scared that everyone
would see how I felt.

332
00:21:12.479 --> 00:21:15.482
I'm a really pathetic human being.

333
00:21:16.483 --> 00:21:17.401
But…

334
00:21:17.484 --> 00:21:21.488
Tani-kun. I want to spend
more time with you.

335
00:21:23.490 --> 00:21:27.744
When you held my hand.
it made me so happy.

336
00:21:27.828 --> 00:21:31.415
So happy that I couldn't
sleep last night and overslept.

337
00:21:31.498 --> 00:21:34.334
I mean. it's sort of like.
"So you did sleep." right?

338
00:21:39.840 --> 00:21:40.674
Suzuki-san.

339
00:21:42.092 --> 00:21:43.176
I…

340
00:21:44.303 --> 00:21:49.016
When you're not talking.
I don't know what to do.

341
00:21:49.725 --> 00:21:53.270
That's the kind
of pathetic human being I am.

342
00:21:55.689 --> 00:21:58.483
Would you… be all right with that?

343
00:22:02.029 --> 00:22:04.823
That face you're making is so adorable!

344
00:22:04.906 --> 00:22:05.907
Hey.

345
00:22:05.991 --> 00:22:07.701
Well. I mean. it's just…

346
00:22:07.784 --> 00:22:11.121
Isn't it obvious?

347
00:22:11.204 --> 00:22:12.706
WAAAHHH

348
00:22:13.623 --> 00:22:16.835
I feel like I've made you cry.

349
00:22:16.918 --> 00:22:18.712
Well. that's because you actually did.

350
00:22:21.631 --> 00:22:24.968
Mascara. was it? It'll come off. right?

351
00:22:27.054 --> 00:22:30.807
You really were listening. weren't you?

352
00:22:30.891 --> 00:22:32.100
This is crazy!

353
00:22:32.184 --> 00:22:35.270
-Huh? Why? What caused it?
-My heart's all fluttery!

354
00:22:35.353 --> 00:22:36.813
{\an8}Oh. honestly!

355
00:22:37.305 --> 00:23:37.222
Do you want subtitles for any video?
